See https://z.arrowfs.org/wiki/ops/Ops_On-call for user manual and on-call guide lines.

How to deploy
====

On the monitor server
----

$ cd /opt
$ git clone <repos_url>/aerofs.pagerduty
$ sudo ln -s /opt/aerofs.pagerduty/cron.daily /etc/cron.daily/pagerduty
$ sudo ln -s /opt/aerofs.pagerduty/cron.hourly /etc/cron.hourly/pagerduty

Finally, change the cron.daily job's time from 0600 to 1400 in /etc/crontab so people are less likely to be waken up at 6AM.

On the meta-monitor server
----

Same as above but instead link meta.cron.hourly to the cron tab
